data.description: 3,600 sf SFH on .526 acres in Greenwood Acres community in Annapolis, 3 BR + Den, 3.5 bath.  Original owner since 1996 added many upgrades added over the years including a 740 sf inground pool that goes from 3' to 8', basement finished with Owings Corning Basement Finishing System which offers acoustic durable walls (valued at over $10,000 and under warranty), fully fenced yard (valued at over $10,000), BOSE surround sound speakers installed in family room.  The garage was converted to a heat/AC serviced fitness center among other countless upgrades.  With a significant down payment, the underlying low interest FHA loan may be assumable.  Paved driveway fits at least 7 cars.  Hardwood floors, open kitchen with breakfast bar, step down family room with skylights & marble wood-burning fireplace, wrap around deck with huge yard.  Honey, we're home!
